lgp.core.program.registers

Class Register<T>

  • lgp.core.program.registers.Register<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of values the register can contain.

    public class Register<T>

    A register that is available to an LGP program.

    Registers contain some value and have a specified index, which defines their position in the context of a class RegisterSet.

    See Also:
    class RegisterSet
